  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个部署流程的状态图。起点应该是Developer，开发者需要同时处理Infrastructure和Kubernetes两块，另外还有个CommonConfig作为中间配置层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Developer是入口。那CommonConfig和Infrastructure、Kubernetes之间是什么关系？是单向依赖还是双向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CommonConfig被Infrastructure和Kubernetes共同引用，但Kubernetes那边其实也会反过来读取CommonConfig做校验，所以这两条可以画成双向。另外CommonConfig最终要驱动Application部署。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把结构搭出来：起点指向Developer，Developer分出三条线到Infrastructure、Kubernetes和CommonConfig。然后CommonConfig连到Application作为终点前的最后一步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但CommonConfig和Kubernetes之间你画的是单向，我刚才说的是双向。还有Infrastructure到CommonConfig也是单向引用对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Infrastructure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "哦对，我漏了Kubernetes回指CommonConfig的那条。现在补上，CommonConfig和Kubernetes之间是双向箭头，Infrastructure到CommonConfig保持单向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Infrastructure"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后Application部署完成后流程就结束了，不需要再指向其他状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，Application指向终点。整个流程：从初始状态进入Developer，开发者并行处理Infrastructure、Kubernetes和CommonConfig，其中CommonConfig与Kubernetes双向交互，Infrastructure单向引用CommonConfig，最终CommonConfig触发Application部署完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
